Package org.apache.daffodil.japi

Class DaffodilParseXMLReader

java.lang.Object
org.apache.daffodil.japi.DaffodilParseXMLReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLReader
public class DaffodilParseXMLReader extends Object implements XMLReader
SAX method of parsing schema and getting the DFDL Infoset via some org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, based on the org.xml.sax.XMLReader interface
